parameters:
\nw[\N[21]]This is the entrance to the underground... I
suppose.

\nw[\N[3]]The water level has been shallow all the way here.
But it's worrisome to be underground with loose
soil in a marshy area, isn't it?

\nw[\N[21]]Hmm... The location of the monsters is definitely
below, huh.

\nw[\N[21]]If the water level is shallow, it's highly likely
that we're underground. But I don't understand why
we came all the way to this place after Rodrigo
was attacked in the first place.

\nw[\N[21]]Even if this is their nest, it's too far from
where they attacked.

\nw[\N[3]]That's right. Their movements are unnatural for a
stray. We should consider the possibility that the
monsters are familiars with a master.

\nw[\N[21]]Seriously... If that's the case, it's
troublesome...

\nw[\N[21]]Yeah... For now, let's have one person go down for
reconnaissance and if it seems safe, we'll proceed
with the exploration.

\nw[\N[21]]Uka and \N[3] have sharp senses for scouting.
Let's leave it to them. Also, be cautious of traps
as there is a possibility of encountering
intelligent opponents.

\nw[\N[21]]Make sure Thorz and Yellow are always ready to
move.

\nw[\N[21]]The walls and ceiling seem sturdy. It doesn't look
like a man-made structure... but it feels
unnatural for something natural to be found
underground in a swamp.
\nw[\N[3]]Maybe the power of the spirits is strong.

\nw[\N[21]]The monsters we're chasing are still further down.
Shall we give it a try and explore?
